name: VersaMix
description:
This model is intented to be versatile enough to generate a wide variety of casual, NSFW, and landscape photos using a single checkpoint model!

Comparison with Popular Models

Below are the results from the x/y plot for comparison between other popular models like chillmix, grapefruit, and realisticvision:

This model appears to produce more natural looking images with a softer tone, this might be due to VAE usage. You can use the 840000 pruned VAE found here: https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/sd-vae-ft-mse

Recommended Parameters

Anime Sampler: DDIM + 2x hires 0.55 noise

Realistic Sampler: DPM++2M Karras

Sampling Steps: 15-25

Clip: 2

Negative Embeddings: versa-simple-neg

I don't have access to a desktop GPU so every sample image was generated on my laptop with an RTX2070 at resolutions no greater than 512x768 (before upscaling).
